; Single-neuron style forward pass with threshold activation.
; x = [2, 3, 1], w = [4, 2, 6], threshold = 20
; weighted_sum = 2*4 + 3*2 + 1*6 = 20
; Output ACC = 1 if weighted_sum == threshold, else 0.
.memory 8
.init 0 2
.init 1 3
.init 2 1
.init 3 4
.init 4 2
.init 5 6
.init 6 20
.init 7 0

LOAD 0
MULM 3
STORE 7

LOAD 1
MULM 4
ADDM 7
STORE 7

LOAD 2
MULM 5
ADDM 7
STORE 7
LOAD 7
SUBM 6
JZ activated

LOADI 0
HALT

activated:
LOADI 1
HALT
